libesmtp: libESMTP (Library for Posting Electronic Mail)
libesmtp:
libesmtp: LibESMTP is a library to manage posting (or submission of)
libesmtp: electronic mail using SMTP to a preconfigured Mail Transport
libesmtp: Agent (MTA) such as Exim or Postfix.  It may be used as part
libesmtp: of a Mail User Agent (MUA) or another program that must be
libesmtp: able to post electronic mail but where mail functionality is
libesmtp: not the program's primary purpose.
